er，而且之前連協恩呢d名校都接洽過佢，佢喺而家呢個市道，以非兩大grad+無pgde，都仲可以人揀工而唔係工揀佢（仲要係名校喎），佢係非一般嘅堅，好令人葡萄的。"},{"pid":"afe309145fb1e6d312b3256abc1a01a326d5c2e5","tid":389610,"uid":53773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:59:09.000Z","msg":"大丁丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7984324577a5cda1587b351eac954f72fb55eea0","tid":389610,"uid":67657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T12:05:55.000Z","msg":"我呢幾日又loop返佢d片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來做左老師喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"019910c33a5092529bc171b978a703482f1d094d","tid":389610,"uid":119379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T17:35:11.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"b2474706bf07cd336a48bdbd71e7306b655e4db5","tid":389610,"uid":53811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:06:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家啲中學生興用微博<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原本個學生係微博出料先<br />\n無得救"},{"pid":"492fc74326651a0152b0a2e353735266e8384a3f","tid":389610,"uid":4213,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:10:58.000Z","msg":"個髮型轉左無咁柒<br />\n期待佢呢啲比人荼毒左嘅人<br />\n繼續用果套On9朗誦方法傳來去<br />\n繼續荼毒下一代<br />\n繼續傳承支那人嘅垃圾文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30de9c3ea72418e8ddb99655343f835a18844177","tid":389610,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:15:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a8e6c16245c02cbab5ca1d4da47e16da7071f45","tid":389610,"uid":131836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:27:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>張愛玲講得好：成名要趁早。<br />\n<br />\n就咁講佢教聖母玫瑰未必反映到佢幾堅，<br />\n如果講埋佢未有pgde 都已經有CM offer，而且之前連協恩呢d名校都接